oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Rodgers family, ca. 1866
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Dr. James Rodgers family, ca. 1866. Dr. James Rodgers is seated at right. Mrs. Rodgers is seated at left. They had ten children; all eight of the living children are in the photograph. Standing second from left is Milton C. Wilcox, who married Belle Rodgers (standing third from left) in 1866.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Group portraits; Families;
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Knox County Two Centuries Photograph Project
